My submission, the X-5 "Firemoth" Executive SSTO;

6.7t dry weight, 14.3t fully fueled. Two RAPIER engines provide plenty of thrust for the climb to orbit, and the outstanding lift characteristics means this can be glided the last 3 km to touchdown.

